oji\" />"},{"pid":"37d7044a0d4ae16ed449293bcd60b8c268cb6bc3","tid":365702,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你同d人話汎垃圾有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncarry唔到就話隻英垃圾</blockquote><br />\n無優點係垃圾"},{"pid":"b58b488a45bd70469ed7e7bfa2805ab87a796df2","tid":365702,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T23:57:28.000Z","msg":"順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"1667398caa5016a1349874be5827f5505abf2529","tid":365702,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:16:57.000Z","msg":"w技用得好<br />\n打rank冇煩惱<br />\n你識條鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93b79c0b4b24b728758910293d4673a5a68fa07","tid":365702,"uid":61529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:56:25.000Z","msg":"其實好多人都玩唔出呢隻英既精髓 呢隻英擺明唔講求同其他英一樣既輸出 而係由一開始瘋狂開W推爆人地"},{"pid":"505dc92697a25f100be776b7513686ea31844f1a","tid":365702,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:22:27.000Z","msg":"仲玩lol係咩心態？"},{"pid":"2f9f8d7ed2b805753e25e102f55ce5ba6bbfc64d","tid":365702,"uid":25086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:36:43.000Z","msg":"推線快,W第一下爆擊彈射全部都爆，後期輸出根本爆炸<br />\nE盾自保,R 成隊加速強開走佬都得<br />\n講到隻英冇用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}